{"tid":1071951,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關 於 「罪 犯 自 新 條 例」嘅 迷 思","createTime":"2019-03-21T16:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:07:55.000Z","uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffa5d2ccd0c757789be9b4e98cc98aeaf6fc283","tid":1071951,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"條例就只係規定罪犯可以唔披露過往<span style=\"color: red;\">定罪</span><br />\n<br />\n咁如果有公司喺職位申請喥寫：<br />\n申請人過往有否被「<span style=\"color: red;\">控告</span>」<br />\n<br />\n而申請人選擇隱瞞並且最後被發現嘅話<br />\n<br />\n公司可唔可以告佢詐騙/追返佢過往嘅人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條例：<br />\n(1)凡個別人士 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)不論在本條例生效之前或之後在香港被定罪，但並未因此被判處監禁超過3個月或罰款超過$10,000； (由1993年第24號第22條修訂)<br />\n(b)在此以前不曾在香港被定罪；及<br />\n(c)經過3年時間並未在香港再被定罪，<br />\n<br />\n則 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)除第3(3)及(4)條另有規定外，在任何程序中均不得接納傾向顯示他在香港曾被如此定罪的證據；<br />\n(ii)就他以往的定罪、罪行、行為或情況而向他或向其他人提出的有關問題，或加諸於他或其他人的有關披露該等定罪、罪行、行為或情況的義務，均須視為並非指該項定罪；及<br />\n(iii)該項定罪或不披露該項定罪，均不得作為將他從任何職位、專業、職業或受僱工作撤除或排除的合法或正當理由，亦不得作為使他在該職位、專業、職業或受僱工作上在任何方面蒙受不利的合法或正當理由。"},{"pid":"184cdebc03df87bedf36cc2e9175732206f21c52","tid":1071951,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"好似係睇你apply既職位而定"},{"pid":"d05d2b0a2c2e55250df34c038dc44f63d8533f5a","tid":1071951,"uid":31076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"184cdebc03df87bedf36cc2e9175732206f21c52","tid":1071951,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"好似係睇你apply既職位而定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"當然唔係講條例所限制嘅職位 e.g. 總薪級表某級以上政府工<br />\n<br />\n純粹係諗到如果有公司用「被控告」嚟捉字失，求職者有無義務講真話<br />\n<br />\n因為自新咗你都係被告過"},{"pid":"dd594f0b8e9bce9ccaaf97e5143feff5227d79f3","tid":1071951,"uid":133828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc0e38feb224762b429cfdff75473b6d70f3e2f","tid":1071951,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd594f0b8e9bce9ccaaf97e5143feff5227d79f3","tid":1071951,"uid":133828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d107bc01c6641ce2ad8c9eba369aa1b202762d","tid":1071951,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"有控告但告唔入又點計"},{"pid":"63217f1d24fbfb4d9d24f8c05bf5fe2c7491b5ae","tid":1071951,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d107bc01c6641ce2ad8c9eba369aa1b202762d","tid":1071951,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"有控告但告唔入又點計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"根據表格上問題應該填&quot;有&quot;"},{"pid":"0c20a3ae30cfec2f0f996546bbd35261b5e188e8","tid":1071951,"uid":1654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b0d107bc01c6641ce2ad8c9eba369aa1b202762d","tid":1071951,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"有控告但告唔入又點計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"比控告不小心駕駛使唔使申報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282cfbedde8fce774f8999bdaee05ea9900b0f4a","tid":1071951,"uid":21961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"63217f1d24fbfb4d9d24f8c05bf5fe2c7491b5ae","tid":1071951,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d107bc01c6641ce2ad8c9eba369aa1b202762d","tid":1071951,"uid":62167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"有控告但告唔入又點計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":